# Frontend Development Rules

## ⚛️ React Frontend Guidelines

### **Application Structure**
- **Main App**: [resume-builder/src/App.js](mdc:resume-builder/src/App.js) - Router configuration and context providers
- **Entry Point**: [resume-builder/src/index.js](mdc:resume-builder/src/index.js) - React DOM rendering
- **Build Config**: [resume-builder/craco.config.js](mdc:resume-builder/craco.config.js) - CRACO configuration for Tailwind

### **Context Management**
- **Auth Context**: [resume-builder/src/contexts/AuthContext.js](mdc:resume-builder/src/contexts/AuthContext.js) - User authentication state
- **Dark Mode**: [resume-builder/src/contexts/DarkModeContext.js](mdc:resume-builder/src/contexts/DarkModeContext.js) - Theme management
- **Global State**: Context-based state management (no Redux)

### **Component Architecture**
- **Layout**: [resume-builder/src/components/Layout.js](mdc:resume-builder/src/components/Layout.js) - Main layout wrapper
- **Protected Routes**: [resume-builder/src/components/ProtectedRoute.js](mdc:resume-builder/src/components/ProtectedRoute.js) - Authentication guards
- **Public Pages**: [resume-builder/src/components/public/](mdc:resume-builder/src/components/public/) - Marketing pages

### **Key Components**
- **Resume Builder**: [resume-builder/src/components/ResumeForm.js](mdc:resume-builder/src/components/ResumeForm.js) - Main resume creation
- **Template Selection**: [resume-builder/src/components/TemplateSelection.js](mdc:resume-builder/src/components/TemplateSelection.js) - Template picker
- **Resume Preview**: [resume-builder/src/components/ResumePreviewEnhanced.js](mdc:resume-builder/src/components/ResumePreviewEnhanced.js) - PDF preview
- **Authentication**: [resume-builder/src/components/login.js](mdc:resume-builder/src/components/login.js) - Login/Register forms

### **Styling Guidelines**
- **Framework**: Tailwind CSS with custom configuration
- **Config**: [resume-builder/tailwind.config.js](mdc:resume-builder/tailwind.config.js) - Tailwind setup
- **PostCSS**: [resume-builder/postcss.config.js](mdc:resume-builder/postcss.config.js) - CSS processing
- **Global Styles**: [resume-builder/src/index.css](mdc:resume-builder/src/index.css) - Base styles

### **Routing Structure**
```javascript
// Public Routes
/ - HomePage
/login - Login
/register - Register
/privacy-policy - Privacy Policy
/terms-conditions - Terms & Conditions

// Protected Routes
/dashboard - ResumeList
/resume-form - ResumeForm
/template-selection/:resumeId - TemplateSelection
/resume-preview/:resumeId - ResumePreviewEnhanced
/subscription - Subscription
/profile - Profile
/analytics - AnalyticsDashboard
```

### **State Management Patterns**
- **Authentication**: Context-based with JWT tokens
- **User Data**: Centralized in AuthContext
- **Theme**: Dark/Light mode with localStorage persistence
- **Form State**: Local component state with controlled inputs

### **API Integration**
- **Base URL**: `process.env.REACT_APP_API_URL` or `http://localhost:5000`
- **Authentication**: JWT tokens in Authorization header
- **Error Handling**: Toast notifications with react-toastify
- **Loading States**: Component-level loading indicators

### **Form Handling**
- **Resume Forms**: Controlled components with validation
- **File Uploads**: Multer integration for profile pictures
- **Validation**: Client-side validation with error messages
- **Submission**: Axios POST requests with error handling

### **UI/UX Guidelines**
- **Responsive Design**: Mobile-first approach with Tailwind breakpoints
- **Accessibility**: ARIA labels and keyboard navigation
- **Loading States**: Skeleton loaders and spinners
- **Error States**: User-friendly error messages
- **Success States**: Toast notifications for actions

### **Performance Optimization**
- **Code Splitting**: React.lazy() for route-based splitting
- **Image Optimization**: WebP format for thumbnails
- **Bundle Size**: Tree shaking and dynamic imports
- **Caching**: Static assets with proper cache headers

### **Development Tools**
- **Build System**: Create React App with CRACO
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS with PostCSS
- **Icons**: Heroicons for consistent iconography
- **Animations**: Lottie animations for loading states

### **Environment Configuration**
```javascript
// Development
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:5000
REACT_APP_ENVIRONMENT=development

// Production
REACT_APP_API_URL=https://your-backend-domain.com
REACT_APP_ENVIRONMENT=production
```

### **Component Patterns**
```javascript
// Functional Components with Hooks
const ComponentName = () => {
  const { user, login, logout } = useAuth();
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);
  
  return (
    <div className="container mx-auto">
      {/* Component JSX */}
    </div>
  );
};

// Protected Route Wrapper
<ProtectedRoute>
  <ComponentName />
</ProtectedRoute>
```

### **Styling Patterns**
```css
/* Tailwind Classes */
.container {
  @apply mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8;
}

.button {
  @apply inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-indigo-500;
}
```

### **Error Handling**
- **Network Errors**: Axios interceptors for global error handling
- **Validation Errors**: Form-level error display
- **Authentication Errors**: Redirect to login page
- **404 Errors**: Custom error page component

### **Mobile Support**
- **Responsive Design**: Tailwind responsive utilities
- **Touch Interactions**: Mobile-friendly button sizes
- **Viewport**: Proper meta tags for mobile rendering
- **PWA Ready**: Service worker configuration for offline support